            <title>[OAK-3089] LIRS cache: zero size cache causes IllegalArgumentException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-3089</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The LIRS cache does not support a zero size cache currently. Such a configuration causes an IllegalArgumentException.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Instead, no exception should be thrown, and no or a minimum size cache should be used.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
